  "texts": [
    "In addition, the details of the guidelines should include both Do's and Dont's, such as the proper ways to use AI-generated materials, and when uncited AI-generated materials would be perceived as plagiarism or academic dishonesty.",
    "On top of that, the guideline should also include what are the university handling procedures and potential penalties, and whether the penalties have a retrospective effect.",
    "Despite Hong Kong public universities being on the restricted list of Open AI for accessing ChatGPT, this study shows that ChatGPT has the potential to \"democratize the power of education\" [30].",
    "Few studies also advocate for promoting the importance of equitable access to ChatGPT for all students.",
    "As innovation is vital and technology plays a huge role in the competitiveness of individuals and countries, it is crucial to have fair access within and between countries to avoid widening any existing technological and educational divides [27,32]."
